## Project Structure

```
src/
├── api/            # Axios config & service calls
├── assets/         # Static assets
├── components/     # Reusable UI components
├── config/         # Firebase config
├── context/        # React Context providers
├── hook/           # Custom hooks
├── interface/      # TypeScript interfaces
├── pages/          # Route page components
├── routes/         # Route config & guards
├── services/       # Business logic services
├── utils/          # Utility functions
├── App.tsx         # Root component
└── main.tsx        # Entry point
```

## Conventions

- Components use `index.tsx` pattern inside their folder (e.g., `components/Header/index.tsx`)
- Pages follow the same `pages/PageName/index.tsx` pattern
- CSS: use Tailwind utility classes; SCSS available via `sass-embedded` but prefer Tailwind
- Alerts via `sweetalert2` — use `Swal.fire()` pattern
- Auth state managed through `authContext.tsx` + `useAuth` hook
- Project state through `ProjectContext.tsx` + `useProject` hook
